This Privacy Policy sets out how we collect and
                        use your personal information when you (i) use
                        the services offered by the Company and its
                        subsidiaries and distributors of the Game as
                        provided by EULA by visiting our website; (ii)
                        use games and the Websites as defined in EULA;
                        and (iii) register an account, if any, (an
