It is reminded that information collected via
                        the Services offered by the Company and its
                        distributors is used by the Company, responsible
                        for its processing.
In case of any contradictions between this
                        Privacy Policy and EULA, this Privacy Policy
                        will prevail.
THIS PRIVACY POLICY
By making the Services available, we, acting
                        reasonably and in good faith, believe that you:
have all necessary rights to register an
                                Account, and use the Services;
provide true information about yourself
                                to the extent necessary for the use of
                                the Services;
understand that, by posting your
                                personal information, if there is such a
                                technical possibility in the Services,
                                and where it is accessible by other
                                users of the Services, you have
                                manifestly made this information public,
                                and this information may become
                                available to other Websites users and
                                Internet users, be copied, and be
                                disseminated by them;
understand that some types of
                                information transferred by you to other
                                Service users cannot be deleted by you
                                or by us;
are aware of and accept this Privacy
                                Policy.
We do not check the user information received
                        from you, except where such a check is necessary
                        in order for us to fulfill our obligations to
                        you.
Please, note that the Websites and/or the
                        Services are not anyhow directed to children
                        under 13 years and when advertising our
                        services, we do not target children. Use of the
                        Services by children requires prior parental
                        control and permission. We do not knowingly
                        obtain personal information of children under 13
                        years.
If you are under 13, please do not use the
                        Services and do not provide any of your
                        information to us, do not create an Account
                        and/or post any of your information on our
                        Websites. If we reveal, that we have
                        unintentionally received personal data of a
                        child under 13 years we will delete the said
                        data.
Should you believe, that we collected personal
                        data of children or the child posted his data
                        within the Websites without relevant parental
                        consent, please contact us, so that we could
                        promptly delete irrelevant data and take all the
                        necessary steps. However, please be aware that
                        in certain cases such
requests may not result in full deletion of
                        respective data.
